    <preface>
      <p class="center"><i>These notes relate to the Regulation of Legal Services (Scotland) Act 2025 (asp 8)</i><br /><i>which received Royal Assent on 27 June 2025</i></p>
      <p class="center"><b>REGULATION OF LEGAL SERVICES (SCOTLAND) ACT 2025</b></p>
      <p class="center"><b>EXPLANATORY NOTES</b></p>
    </preface>
    <mainBody>
