              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>27th Meeting 2023 (12 December 2023) (In private)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><a href="https://www.parliament.scot/chamber-and-committees/committees/current-and-previous-committees/session-6-equalities-human-rights-and-civil-justice-committee/meetings/2023/ehrcjs62327/minutes"><u>SP M Equalities, Human Rights and Civil Justice Committee 12 December 2023</u></a>, para 3</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>2nd Meeting 2024 (23 January 2024) (In private)</p>
